	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p><addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Curacao</placeName> <date>8 Sept 1859</date></p>
				<p>Dear Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Your esteemed lines of the<lb/> <date>26 July</date> is duly received&#44; where I noted with<lb/> much pleasure your good health &#38;c<lb/>  The object of this is to inform you that with<lb/> this date I remit to <persName>Messrs Dovale &#38; Co</persName> Ninety<lb/> four dollars 80&#47;00 to be forward to you for my a&#47;c<lb/> which sum is of 5 <sic>setts</sic> books I sold&#44; as specify&#8222;<lb/>&#8222;ing here below&#44; this time I had to make a discount<lb/> of 10 pct.  I hope you will be satisfied&#59; I think<lb/> to have soon another order for some <sic>setts</sic>&#44; I will<lb/> advice you to send 3 setts of Prayers books and 3 of Pen<lb/>tateuchs as it remains none in hand.  I request<lb/> you to send me one copy of <persName>Bendeman&#39;s</persName> &#8220;<persName>Jere<lb/>miah</persName> on the ruins of <placeName><sic>Jerusalm</sic></placeName>&#8221; also one edi<lb/>&#8222;tion of select sentences&#44; their value shall be re<lb/>&#8222;mitted immediately.  I send you <sic>inclose</sic> some<lb/> information regarding our <hi rend="underline">Medrash</hi> I hope<lb/> it will deserve a place in your periodical.<lb/>  <persName>Hoham Chaimaeiro<add>&#63;</add></persName> send his good wishes to you<lb/> without further for the present I am yours &#38;c</p>
				<p><persName role="author">B. de Casseres Jr</persName></p>
				<p><hi rend="underline">Note</hi></p>
				<table rows="8" cols="2">
				<row>
				<cell>2 setts Prayers books &#40;<add>&#63;</add>&#41;</cell>
				<cell>&#36;48</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>1 &#8220;<add>&#63;</add> <add>&#63;</add></cell>
				<cell>20</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>2 &#8220;Pentateuch</cell>
				<cell><hi rend="underline">24</hi></cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell>&#36;92</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>10 &#37; Discount on them</cell>
				<cell><hi rend="underline">  9.20</hi></cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell>&#36;82.80</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>4 subscribers of occid&#58;</cell>
				<cell><hi rend="underline"> 12</hi></cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell>&#36;94.80</cell>
				</row>
				</table>
				<p>Turn Over</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>As I am missing the first four Volumes<lb/> of the Occident to have them all complete&#44; I beg<lb/> you to let me have those volumes by first<lb/> opportunity&#44; and let me know their value.</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p><addressee>Isaac Leeser Esqr</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi></placeName></p>
				<p>care <persName>Messrs Dovale &#38; Co.</persName></p>
		</body>
